#!/usr/bin/env python
"""
This is the new gateway program to all of the cgns_utils.

Run cgns_utils -help to get a list of all available options. The basic
idea is as follows:

                                              | write new file
read cngs file -> Do some operations on it -> |     .or.
                                              | write modified file
Developed by Dr. Gaetan K. W. Kenway
"""
